"ANTI MAGIC SHELL"
 
Usage       : cast 'anti-magic shell' 
Accumulative: No
Duration    : 1 Hour.
Level       : Level 48 Mage.
Save        : None
 
        This spell enables the caster to shell him/herself from ANY magic
force. However, it also prevents the caster from using any magic spells of
his/her own as well.
 
 
